data.description: Welcome home to 531! As you walk in the front door, you're welcomed by an open living room with a cozy fireplace. To your right is a bedroom that could also be used as an office area. The living room runs into a spacious dining room. The kitchen features a pantry and plenty of counter space. The laundry room is in the back of the house featuring a basement, providing peace of mind during inclement weather. This home has gorgeous hardwood floors, light updates, and so much room for more customization. The backyard features a large detached garage that's been used as a workshop. Schedule your private tour today!
